cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY

This paper deals with sentiment analysis of customer reviews, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The use of neural networks for this task suggests that it could be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for extracting relevant information from unstructured text, which could also place it under cs.IR. The use of machine learning algorithms for sentiment analysis could also suggest categories such as cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper's focus on customer reviews and their impact on businesses could potentially place it under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
